--- Switchblade ---
Switchblade's smile widdens even more as he surveys the 
battlefield. "Hmmm..." His visor slides away to reveal his green 
eyes. They eyes look penetraitingly into the monitors as Switchblade 
thinks, <<Maybe, just maybe Prowl will take care of Megatron for 
me...>> Though that's not likely, Firestrike is there to ensure his 
survival... nevertheless, there is always the chance>>. Switchblade 
sits back in the command chair with his feet kicked back and he 
continues to think.
